---

<section
  id="tech-leading-ladies"
  aria-label="Tech Leading Ladies"
  class="py-16 sm:py-20 border-t"
  style="border-color: var(--color-border)"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[680px] px-6 sm:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mb-7">Tech Leading Ladies</h2>

    <div class="space-y-5 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Tech Leading Ladies is a community for women-identifying and non-binary people in software
        development and technology roles — with a specific focus on stepping into and thriving in
        technical leadership.
      </p>
      <p>
        What started as a coaching circle has grown into a community of nearly 2,000 members across
        Australia and New Zealand, with 76+ events, an active mentoring program, and a Slack
        community where real conversations happen.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you've ever been made to feel like you're not quite technical enough, not quite senior
        enough, or not quite the right fit — this community is for you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-10 border-t" style="border-color: var(--color-border)">
      <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Recent event</h3>
      <p class="text-sm mb-5" style="color: var(--color-ink-muted)">Intention Setting Workshop · February 2026</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
        <img
          src="/images/susan-speaking-tll-2026-1.jpeg"
          alt="Susan Brander facilitating the Tech Leading Ladies intention setting workshop, February 2026"
          class="w-full sm:w-48 rounded-lg object-cover flex-shrink-0"
          style="aspect-ratio: 3/4; object-position: top"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-ink-muted)">
          With 2026 well under way, we paused to make sure we had everything we needed to make it
          a great year. I guided the group through reflection time, exploring where everyone was at
          and what they most wanted from the year ahead — then we set some intentions and paths
          forward together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3" role="list">
      <a
        href="https://techleadingladies.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        role="listitem"
        class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md font-medium text-sm no-underline hover:no-underline transition-colors"
      >
        Visit Tech Leading Ladies
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.meetup.com/tech-leading-ladies/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        role="listitem"
        class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-md font-medium text-sm no-underline hover:no-underline border transition-colors"
      >
        Join on Meetup
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    border-color: var(--color-border);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
